    "description": "For a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5, confirmation of absolute hemolysis index predictions against the clinical threshold must be supported by experimental-validation activities. Physical flow-loop measurements with controlled inlet conditions and calibrated haematological assays are required to establish the validation evidence base. Computational reproduction of previously published results does not satisfy this requirement unless accompanied by independent bench-top experimental corroboration.",
